# VIBECODER MASTER RULES — Quiet Partner

## Stack (Vibe Stack 2026)

- **Frontend:** Next.js 16 (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v4, shadcn/ui, Zustand, Recharts
- **Backend:** Next.js API routes (BFF for DeepSeek / Gemini) — **no API keys on client**
- **Database:** deferred post–Phase 0 (PostgreSQL if persistence needed)

## Agent behavior

- Read `orchestration-queue.md` before work; update on finish.
- Plan in **3 short steps** before coding.
- Match patterns in `docs/tech-stack.md` — **not Vite** (legacy DeepSeek dialogue discarded).

## Structure

- `app/` — routes and API BFF
- `components/` — UI including DomainRadar, HealthCommentary
- `lib/` — system prompt, store helpers
- `knowledge-base/` — product + PMBOK playbook
- `docs/` — roadmap, **implementation-plan.md**

## Quality gate

Before commit (when Human asks): types, no secret leakage, build/lint, disclaimer «co-pilot not cert tool» on user-facing AI copy.
